YA_NL%NREQIN.Extra info: For NWP clouds are resolved very rapidly because the humidity is coupled,

YQ_NL%LGP.Explenation: Is humidity in grippoint space? (reverse of YQ_NL%LSP)
YQ_NL%LGP.Extra info: ATTENTION! if i am correct, ALARO stores humidity in GP space, AROME in SP, so adjust according to your BD model!

YQ_NL%LSP.Explenation: Is humidity in spectral space? (reverse of YQ_NL%LGP)
YQ_NL%LSP.Extra info: ATTENTION! if i am correct, ALARO stores humidity in GP space, AROME in SP, so adjust according to your BD model!

YQ_NL%NREQIN.Extra info: Set to 1 so that humidity is interpolated --> needed for clouds --> precipitation types

CSTOP.Extra info: The duration in the numer of timesteps
